  "system": {
    "description": "<p>If you’ve been somewhere before, it’s always close by. Whenever you are moving, you can arrive at any other location you’ve ever been to when you stop. This includes all kinds of moving: running, falling, riding.</p><p>No-one else comes with you. You have precise control over where you appear, but you arrive fully and obviously to anyone present and have no way to look ahead at what’s there.</p><p>If the location has dramatically changed and you move into a place that now has an obstruction, you will appear inside that obstruction and potentially die as a result.</p><p>In addition <strong>Stich</strong> and <strong>I Know a Shortcut</strong> are enhanced.</p>",
